        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"Here we be!\" he croaked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Mary Cox pulled open the door and the first newcomer popped out as though she had been clinging to the handle when The Fox made the movement.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"We will lead the march.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000022_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000022_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "We will take you to the office of the Preceptress.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"Yes!\" agreed Sarah Fish, one of the Infants just arrived.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000034_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000034_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"Two of them came into our room at once-the girl they call The Fox, and Miss Steele.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000034_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000034_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I don't want either.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"I think it would be nicer for us Infants, as they call us, to keep together.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"Hear! hear!\" cried Miss Fish.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000038_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000038_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I, for one, want to get into the real school society----\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "It would look silly,\" cried Helen.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"We won't keep the older girls out of it, if they want to join,\" laughed Sarah.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Most of the girls laughed at that.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_273050_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/273050/8545_273050_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "And the suggestion of a separate club for the Infants seemed to be well received.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"AUNT HANNAH MOORE.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "If such were her calculations she was greatly mistaken.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "For although Aunt Hannah was destitute of book learning she was nevertheless a woman of thought and natural ability, and while she wisely kept her counsel from her mistress she took care to make her wants known to an abolitionist.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000016_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000016_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "The store keeper quickly made known her condition at the Anti slavery Office, and in double quick time j m",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000016_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000016_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "In the eyes of the mistress this procedure was so extraordinary that she became very much excited and for a moment threatened them with the \"broomstick,\" but her raving had no effect on Messrs.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000016_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000016_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "McKim and Wise, who did not rest contented until Aunt Hannah was safely in their hands.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000016_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000016_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "It was prior to her coming into the possession of Moore that Aunt Hannah had been made to drink the bitter waters of oppression.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000016_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000016_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "From this point, therefore, we shall present some of the incidents of her life, from infancy, and very nearly word for word as she related them:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"Moore bought me from a man named McCaully, who owned me about a year.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I fared dreadful bad under McCaully.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "One day in a rage he undertook to beat me with the limb of a cherry tree; he began at me and tried in the first place to snatch my clothes off, but he did not succeed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "After that he beat the cherry tree limb all to pieces over me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I crept out of doors and throwed up blood; some days I was hardly able to creep. With this beating I was laid up several weeks.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Another time Mistress McCaully got very angry.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "One day she beat me as bad as he did.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "She was a woman who would get very mad in a minute.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "One day she began scolding and said the kitchen wasn't kept clean.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "She soon ordered me to come in to her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I went in as she ordered me; she met me with a mule rope, and ordered me to cross my hands.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I crossed my hands and she tied me to the bedstead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000019",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000019.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "He said to his wife she has begged and begged and you have whipped her enough.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000021",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000021.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "The little girl was not able to do it; mr McCaully then untied me himself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000017_000022",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000017_000022.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Both times that I was beat the blood run down from my head to my feet.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "\"They wouldn't give you anything to eat hardly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "He could tell all about how he was kidnapped, but could not find anybody to do anything for him, so he had to content himself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "He was afraid I was going to die, or he would lose me, and I would not be of any service to him, so he took and traded me off for a wagon.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I was something better when he traded me off; well enough to be about.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "My health remained bad for about four years, and I never got my health until Moore bought me. Moore took me for a debt.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I was not born in Missouri but was born in Virginia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "From my earliest memory I was owned by Conrad Hackler; he lived in Grason County.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Hackler bought me from a man named William Scott.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I must go back by good rights to the beginning and tell all: Scott bought me first from a young man he met one day in the road, with a bundle in his arms.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Scott, wishing to know of the young man what he had in his bundle, was told that he had a baby.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "'What are you going to do with it?' said Scott.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Scott offered the young man a horse for it, and the young man took him up.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "This is the way I was told that Scott came by me.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I never knowed anything about my mother or father, but I have always believed that my mother was a white woman, and that I was put away to save her character; I have always thought this.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Under Hackler I was treated more like a brute than a human being.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000021",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000021.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "A bed of straw and old rags was made for me in a big trough called the tan trough (a trough having been used for tanning purposes).",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000022",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000022.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "The cats about the place came and slept with me, and was all the company I had.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000023",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000023.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I had to work with the hoe in the field and help do everything in doors and out in all weathers.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000026",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000026.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "After I growed up to be a woman my master thought nothing of taking my clothes off, and would whip me until the blood would run down to the ground.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000027",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000027.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "After I was twenty five years old they did not treat me so bad; they both professed to get religion about that time; and my master said he would never lay the weight of his finger on me again. Once after that mistress wanted him to whip me, but he didn't do it, nor never whipped me any more.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000028",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000028.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "After awhile my master died; if they had gone according to law I would have been hired out or sold, but my mistress wanted to keep me to carry on the place for her support.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000029",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000029.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "So I was kept for seven or eight years after his death.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000030",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000030.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "It was understood between my mistress, and her children, and her friends, who all met after master died, that I was to take care of mistress, and after mistress died I should not serve anybody else.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000031",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000031.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I done my best to keep my mistress from suffering.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000032",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000032.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "After a few years they all became dissatisfied, and moved to Missouri.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000034",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000034.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Without means they lived as poor people commonly live, on small farms in the woods.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000035",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000035.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "I still lived with my mistress.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000019_000036",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000019_000036.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Some of the heirs got dissatisfied, and sued for their rights or a settlement; then I was sold with my child, a boy.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "The half of what she passed through in the way of suffering has scarcely been hinted at in this sketch.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Fifty seven years were passed in bondage before she reached Philadelphia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000020_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000020_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Gillingham's), whose hearts had been in deep sympathy with the slave for many years.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000020_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000020_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Her mind was deeply imbued with religious feeling, and an unshaken confidence in God as her only trust; she connected herself with the a m e",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000020_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000020_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Bethel Church, of Philadelphia, where she has walked, blameless and exemplary up to this day.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000020_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000020_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "Probably there is not a member in that large congregation whose simple faith and whose walk and conversation are more commendable than Aunt Hannah's.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8545_287671_000020_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8545/287671/8545_287671_000020_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8545",
        "content": "The name of the recipient of the good Quaker friend's bounty and Aunt Hannah's companion, was Thomas Todd.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    }
]